name: Nautes Bedside Table
description: Behind its distinct simplicity, the Nautes bedside table meets the challenge of combining clean lines with the functionality of a piece of furniture needed for placing and storing objects. With perfect proportions and the subtle contrast of oak, wirebrushed and lacquer, the Nautes bedside cabinet has a handy drawer that is almost invisible as it is cleverly integrated into the design. Destined to become a classic, this indispensable piece of bedroom furniture comes in two sizes.
